    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just smile and establish trust.",
      "zh": "只要微笑並建立信任。",
      "ja": "ただ笑顔で信頼を築いて。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi there.",
      "zh": "嗨，朋友。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, little fella.",
      "zh": "嘿，小傢伙。",
      "ja": "やあ、小さなやつ。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You want to do some flap flap today?",
      "zh": "你今天想拍翅膀嗎？",
      "ja": "今日は羽ばたきたい？",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, sure you do.",
      "zh": "喔，你當然想。",
      "ja": "ああ、もちろんだろう。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh, all you do is you just, um, you just flap your wings like this.",
      "zh": "呃，你只要這樣拍動你的翅膀。",
      "ja": "えっと、君がすることはただこうやって羽をばたつかせるだけ。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "zh": "不，不，不，不，不。",
      "ja": "ダメ、ダメ、ダメ、ダメ、ダメ。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "None of that.",
      "zh": "不要那樣。",
      "ja": "そんなのダメ。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on.",
      "zh": "來吧。",
      "ja": "さあ。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All we got to do is, ow.",
      "zh": "我們只要，哎喲。",
      "ja": "やることはただ、あ痛。",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm going to get you.",
      "zh": "我要抓住你。",
      "ja": "君を捕まえるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then another cup of corn.",
      "zh": "然後再來一杯玉米。",
      "ja": "そしてもう一杯のトウモロコシ。",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All we got to do is, ow.",
      "zh": "我們只要，哎喲。",
      "ja": "やることはただ、あ痛。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look.",
      "zh": "看。",
      "ja": "見て。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm going to love with you, okay?",
      "zh": "我會愛你的，好嗎？",
      "ja": "君を愛するよ、いい？",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I kind of bombed out on the whole water and light fairy things.",
      "zh": "我在水和光的仙子那部分搞砸了。",
      "ja": "水と光の妖精のことはちょっと失敗した。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I'm starting to run out of options here.",
      "zh": "我開始沒什麼選擇了。",
      "ja": "もう選択肢がなくなってきた。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You could see fit to flap your little wings and take flight for a few.",
      "zh": "你可以試著拍動你的小翅膀飛一會兒。",
      "ja": "君は小さな翼をばたつかせて少し飛ぶことができるかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Measley seconds.",
      "zh": "短短幾秒。",
      "ja": "わずかな数秒。",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I might be able to go to mainland and bring happiness to the world.",
      "zh": "我或許能去大陸，帶給世界幸福。",
      "ja": "本土に行って世界に幸せをもたらせるかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do you say?",
      "zh": "你怎麼說？",
      "ja": "どう思う？",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wrong answer.",
      "zh": "答錯了。",
      "ja": "間違った答えだ。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shh.",
      "zh": "噓。",
      "ja": "シー。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, if I can't have making eight corn kettles for the rest of my life, I'm holding you personally responsible.",
      "zh": "喔，如果我不能一輩子做八個玉米壺，我會親自追究你的責任。",
      "ja": "ああ、一生八つのトウモロコシケトルを作れないなら、君を個人的に責任を取らせる。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "HOO!",
      "zh": "呼！",
      "ja": "フー！",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    }
  ]
}